<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - PC Builder</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:wght@400;500;600&family=Source+Sans+Pro:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/ae8f1db1af.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: black;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        .topbar {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,0.95), rgba(70,60,111,0.95));
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(138,43,226,0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }

        .flex-container-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 3rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .product-name {
            position: relative;
        }

        .product-name a {
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .product-name h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #8A2BE2, #4B0082);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            position: relative;
        }

        .product-name h3::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8A2BE2, transparent);
        }

        .elements {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .txt-space {
            position: relative;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .txt-space a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }

        .txt-space h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .txt-space:hover h3 {
            color: #8A2BE2;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .txt-space::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: #8A2BE2;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .txt-space:hover::after {
            width: 80%;
        }

        .active {
            background: rgba(138,43,226,0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .active h3 {
            color: #8A2BE2;
        }

        .build-sec {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 7rem 2rem 2rem;
        }

        .build-pictx {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .build-pictx h1 {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .pre-cust-sec {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .pc-option {
            width: 300px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .pc-option:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .pc-option img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .about-us {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 3rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .about-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-content h2 {
            color: #8A2BE2;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .about-content p {
            color: #ccc;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .build-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            background: #463C6F;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .build-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="topbar">
            <div class="flex-container-left">
                <span class="product-name centre-txt">
                    <a href="/">
                        <h3>Build<span style="color: white;">-IT</span></h3>
                    </a>       
                </span>
                <div class="elements flex-container-right">
                    <span class="txt-space centre-txt active">
                        <a href="">
                            <h3>Build your own PC</h3>
                        </a>
                    </span>
                    <span class="txt-space centre-txt">
                        <a href="/doc">
                            <h3>Documentation</h3>
                        </a>
                    </span>
                    <span class="txt-space centre-txt">
                        <a href="/prebuild">
                            <h3>Custom</h3>
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="build-sec">
        <div class="build-pictx">
            <h1>Finding perfect match to your desktop needs made easy</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="pre-cust-sec">
            <a href="/prebuild" class="pc-option">
                <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/mid-end1-removebg-preview-JHZ14H9XqeT9gnnf3u4OqmkekV5hqG.png" alt="Mid-Range Gaming PC">
            </a>
            <a href="/prebuild" class="pc-option">
                <img src="../images/low-end1-removebg-preview.png" alt="Entry-Level Gaming PC">
            </a>
            <a href="/prebuild" class="pc-option">
                <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/ehigh_end-removebg-preview-0nnkU3dBTgjKie4LJzysHWHTBnfuYX.png" alt="High-End Gaming PC">
            </a>
        </div>
        <button class="build-button" onclick="location.href='./build'">
            Build Your Own
        </button>
    </section>

    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to PC Builder, your ultimate destination for custom-built PCs. Whether you're a gaming enthusiast, a professional content creator, or someone who simply needs a high-performance workstation, we help you find the perfect match for your needs.</p>
            <p>Our platform provides a seamless experience in selecting and assembling the best components to build your dream PC. From pre-built configurations to complete customization, we ensure that you get the most out of your budget and requirements.</p>
            <p>Join us today and start building the PC you've always wanted!</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>

